OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJohn Lewis to end 'Never   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FKnowingly Undersold' price 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpledge                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Department store chain John Lewis has  
OL,6, said it will drop its "Never Knowingly 
OL,7, Undersold" price pledge this summer.   
OL,9,FThe price promise, which began in 1925,
OL,10,Fmeans the retailer matches prices on   
OL,11,Fbranded products with national         
OL,12,Fretailers, but not online-only sales.  
OL,14,FJohn Lewis said the pledge was becoming
OL,15,Fless relevant as shopping moves        
OL,16,Fincreasingly online.                   
OL,18,FInstead, the employee-owned retailer   
OL,19,Fsays it will spend #500m on keeping    
OL,20,Fprices down.                           
